message.body: @Nur1o Valid inputs are a, b, z, l, r, start, cup, cdown, cleft, cright, dup, ddown, dleft, dright, up, down, left and right. Directions can be replaced with cardinal directions (n, s, w, e, north, south, east, west). Up to 3 buttons can be pressed simultaneously: "b+up+right". End your input with "-" to hold the buttons down for a longer (266 milliseconds) period than normal (133 milliseconds): "a+z+right-". Commands are not case sensitive: Typing "left" and "lEft" have the same effect.
